          <br></br>
            <h2><b>MTaaS Crowdsourcing</b></h2>
        <p>'Pivoting is not the end of the disruption process, but the beginning of the next leg of your journey'. Welcome to the era of MTaaS Crowdsourcing. The key benefit of crowdsourcing today is speed! You can bring better innovation to market FASTER! Crowdsourcing connects people with the latest ideas and best practices in crowdsourcing and the crowd economy.</p>
		<p><input class ="btn btn-info btn-lg" type="submit" ng-click="login()" value = "App Provider">
